{"tid":799244,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"再創世紀pakho好有型","createTime":"2018-08-30T02:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T07:06:38.000Z","uid":32051,"like":22,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"539099163b5cdf6661f9389cc230b0017eceeecd","tid":799244,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"睇預告果句：以後都唔關我事呀<br />\n<br />\n真係好帶動到觀眾情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就知pakho今次劍指視帝寶座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係睇親預告都覺得好熱血，每次睇緊新聞台見到佢播依個預告都想依一幕早多幾秒俾我睇，最好就重loop幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然未知劇情，但睇到pakho咁出力去飾演一個弱智人士，我覺得佢為藝術犧牲好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好希望佢今次為藝術犧牲，會有所回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f739012d86450fca658bfee3545671b2ad1e8e6e","tid":799244,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T02:17:50.000Z","msg":"做返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60fe15509ab70698aff501317bd2ef8d5ebda2b","tid":799244,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T02:20:37.000Z","msg":"梗係型啦<br />\n套套都做自己 套套都係果個比比鳥頭look<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723ca3b2407ff9eccfed9d3497b5d737ead50c4a","tid":799244,"uid":32051,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f739012d86450fca658bfee3545671b2ad1e8e6e","tid":799244,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T02:17:50.000Z","msg":"做返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T02:34:40.000Z","msg":"超弱智級既演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc6ba098da5ec2bdc62387f38461d3334e44fd2","tid":799244,"uid":32051,"like"